The Following Directory Structure is Usually Followed :

Project-Directory
	|
	|--	run.py
	|-- app/
		|
		| -- static/
		| -- templates/
		| -- __init__.py
		| -- views.py

app Folder contains the application package.
static has static sub-files like JavaScript, Images and CSS
templates folder has the Templates

__init__.py is to initialize the app.

views.py contains various routes.

run.py starts the development server with our application